EXPLORATION RESULTS . The information required to be disclosed includes a drill hole table for all material drill holes, if the information is material to understanding the Exploration Results.  Rule 11.4.1(3) states that the drill hole table must include, in tabular form, the following:

a)	easting and northing of the drill hole collar;

b)	elevation or RL of the drill hold collar;

c)	dip and azimuth of the hole;

d)	down hole width and depth; and

e)	end of hole;

